SUMMARY:Information: Tottenham Hale Station: Tottenham Hotspur vs Burnley 
 at Tottenham Hotspur Stadium on Saturday 16 August (1500 start): Tottenham
  Hale station is expected to be extremely busy between 1300 and 1430 and 
 between 1700 and 1830. You may find it easier to use Northumberland Park 
 station where additional Greater Anglia and Stansted Express trains will 
 call before and after the match\, please board one of the front 7 coaches 
 for Northumberland Park.
END:VEVENT
